<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Where do modern social institutions come from? The genesis of many institutions and concepts can be traced back to the medieval and early modern period. Study this remarkable period for a unique vantage point as we approach the conflicts and challenges of our modern world.</p>
]]>
